description: The ultimate in city loft living, this incredible open-concept brick & beam unit is chic, offers every amenity (2 garage pkg!) & has an amazing private roofdeck that's tough to beat! Situated just over the bridge from Ink Block & the South End, 9 W Broadway is a concierge building w/ gym, garage parking & elevator. Penthouse 601 is an impressive space w/ large, dramatic rooms, exposed brick & beam, outstanding city views & sunlight, & soaring high ceilings. A Poggenpohl kitchen is well-equipped w/ high-end appliances & an excellent layout, including a pantry. The living/dining space is nearly 28 ft & large enough to accommodate multiple seating areas, home office needs, etc. The primary suite is oversized w/ 4 windows, a corner exposure and outfitted walk-in closet. The 2nd/3rd bedrooms offer more wonderful views & are nicely proportioned. Take in the outstanding views from the spectacular & beautifully landscaped private deck w/ built-in grill. Central air, laundry, 2 garage pkg.
